  "texts": [
    "During the collaboration of humans with robots, it is fundamental to hand over products to each other.",
    "Traditional MIP has some drawbacks, such as failing to meet the growing requirements listed below.• In the existing models, the assistive robots only mimic humans, but in the present, the robot is also required to predict human intention with manual intervention.",
    "Hence, in this work, human intention prediction in human-robot interaction is developed based on an adaptive learning network.",
    "• Human action is in quick form and results in uncertainties regarding the accurate representation of the environment.",
    "This research work utilizes the predictive technique for human motion identification to solve this issue."
